name: Ceviche de Pescadilla
description:
I live by the sea
and my friends from here go fishing
then we all eat them fresh fishes
natural local food and frens
we do a lot of ceviche
a food from Peru which consists on
raw fish, a lot of lemon and chopped lil raw vegetables
like onion, pepper, cilander, and can add some fruit
like kiwi or apple
